ygData.messageBody:
The sharkskin tubing or whatever its name was never dropped on sharks as far
as I know. That rumour ran on this list for a long LONG time, but it was
started by someone who had never seen it. He had only been told by someone
that claimed 200 skill a long time ago. That 200 skill person was pretty
flamed on this list for lying and holding back information although he
himself was never here and me for one, and I've been tinkering since I
started my char over a year ago although my skill is still pretty low, have
never heard of it from anywhere but that obscure source on this list quite a
long time ago..

And as someone mentioned earlier, NO chars were moved over from beta, we all
had to start fresh (Sadly, I had a p3 account, hehe)

-Sandortien, newbie lvl 50 wizard of Xegony
